        "text_AcStr8": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>\"<em>What is that thing on your belt?</em>\" — That's exactly what Rohit's team asked him one afternoon at a construction site in Noida.</p><p>He unclipped it, held it up, and smiled. \"AeroClip FrostClip. 10,000mAh. Three months, every single day. <strong>Neck fans are a joke compared to this.</strong>\"</p><p>His colleagues placed orders before lunch was over. And within a week, it had spread through the entire team.</p><p>The reason? <strong>When you clip it to your waist, turbo airflow channels upward through your shirt — cooling your entire torso, not just your chin.</strong> Not a gimmick. The cooling is instant and the difference is real.</p>",
            "text_size": 16,
            "text_color": "#1d1d1d",
            "highlighted_text_color": "#000000",
