        "text_AcFaq0": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2><strong>Frequently Asked Questions</strong></h2><p><strong>❓ Is Cash on Delivery (COD) available?</strong><br/>Yes. We offer COD across most Indian pin codes. Pay online for an additional 10% prepaid discount.</p><p><strong>❓ How long does delivery take?</strong><br/>3–7 business days depending on your city. Delhi, Mumbai, Bangalore, Chennai, Hyderabad typically 3–4 days.</p><p><strong>❓ Can it actually cool me in 45°C heat?</strong><br/>Yes — it won't replicate 22°C AC, but it significantly drops your <em>perceived body temperature</em> by channelling cool airflow against your core. Most users say the difference is between \"uncomfortable\" and \"totally manageable\".</p><p><strong>❓ How loud is it on different speeds?</strong><br/>Speed 1–2 are near-silent — suitable for offices. Speed 4–5 are audible like a table fan on medium. Most outdoor use is perfect on speed 3.</p><p><strong>❓ What is the return policy?</strong><br/>7-day hassle-free returns. If it doesn't work as described, contact our support and we'll resolve it immediately. No questions asked.</p><p><strong>❓ How do I charge it?</strong><br/>Standard USB-C charging. Fully charged in 3–4 hours. The LED battery display shows your exact charge level at all times.</p>",
            "text_size": 15,
