        "text_AcCls1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2><strong>The Bottom Line</strong></h2><p>Summer in India is brutal. And it's getting hotter every year.</p><p>You can't always be near an AC. You can't always avoid going outside. But you <em>can</em> stop letting the heat drain you — physically and mentally.</p><p>The AeroClip FrostClip isn't magic. It's engineering. <strong>10,000mAh of power. Turbo airflow aimed where it actually cools. Completely hands-free. Emergency powerbank built in.</strong></p><p>For ₹2,499, this is the most practical summer purchase you'll make this year.</p><p>⚠️ <em>Stock runs low fast during peak summer. If you're seeing this, it's still available — but don't wait until your neighbour has one.</em></p>",
